&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;在华为服务器上硬装Proxmox时可能会出现以上问题，&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;切换到tty2可以发现报错&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/a103840d-6f4f-43c8-8ba3-978275252707/b5944fa4-d85f-4999-b7ef-ad5f5faac797/Untitled.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;amp;X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45GO43JXI4%2F20241111%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;amp;X-Amz-Date=20241111T084115Z&amp;amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;amp;X-Amz-Signature=cd0a6289aa9b39c5d9227ca8334d74f88d72593e9a87a70139e8c610b1f0303b&amp;amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;amp;x-id=GetObject&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
